data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to check out this home on FORTY ACRES! This home is waiting for you to bring your finishing touches and features the primary bedroom with adjoining bathroom aw well as a Jack and Jill bathroom connecting two other bedrooms. This 4 bed 3 bath home also sports tons of storage and an additional large room that can be used as  a den or office. The property boasts a seasonal pond, oversized garage, 2 outbuildings, a dog run(!) and kennels, and tons of space, perfect for the outdoor enthusiast. There's plenty of room for the shooting range and off roading and even an old greyhound race track on the property.  Property is being sold As-Is condition.
